description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=0/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=0/3. You tend to a farm of squeebels. Using unique A.I. to grow and prosper. They will seek out food sources,  friends and mates, and pass on their genetics to their children.  Manipulate the way they turn out by growing different plant species for them to eat or separate them out for even more control , what you choose to do is entirely up to you! The possibilities are virtually endless.
